			<p style="font-size:20px"><center>&ndash;Late Shree PannaLal Ji Maharaj Sa&ndash;</center></p>
			<h1 style="font-size:19px;">History</h1>
			<p >Shree Pragya Mrigi Rog Nivarak Samiti was established on September 21, 1978. The idea of opening this organisation is inspired by Late Shree 1008 Shree Kudndanmal Ji Maharaj Sa and in the rememberance of Late Shree 1008 Shree PannaLal ji Maharaj Sa.</p>
			<p>The Organisation is serving the patients of Epilepsy from Last 36 Years And Successful in providing satisfactory results. The journey was started with only 4 patients initially. And it is proud for all of us now that organisation is growing with total 36000 patients which is extremely tremendous. According to a Survey, 80% of the patients are cured of it and living a happy life. Approximately 4500 patients every month are taking the treatment and getting fruitful results. People from Different States including Rajasthan, Madhya Pradesh, Maharashtra, Punjab, Tamil Nadu, Karnataka, Gujrat, Andra Pradesh, Haryana, Punjab, Bihar, Chattisgarh and from abroad are restoring to their health.</p>
